description: There’s no balla like snoballas because they’re bringing deliciously refreshing New Orleans-style sno balls through the streets of Jackson!Handmade and high fructose corn syrup-free, these fluffy flavorful icy treats are fantastic for any occasion. You’ll also find cotton candy, chili dogs, and many other of your favorite concessions. Invite this fun truck to your next big party and have yourselves a ball!
name: Snoballas
